--- !u!1001 &1098753527
PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Queen: States if they are next to at least one ghost. If lying, will
        only state they are next to ghosts if surrounded by subjects


        Maid:
        States a character is a ghost. Will always select subjects if lying. If she
        picks herself, she is a lying subject


        Nun: States two potential
        subjects the ghost could be. Will select multiple ghosts if possible, and
        will only select subjects if lying. If she picks herself, she is a lying
        subject


        Priest: Only one of three characters is a ghost. If lying,
        none of them are. If he picks himself, he is telling the truth


        Knight:
        the second character is a ghost if and only if the first is a subject. If
        lying, the second character is always a subject. If he picks himself, he
        is a lying subject'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSize
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 564308043685198918, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_HorizontalAlignment
      value: 1
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 649765280201625091, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: 'Blacksmith: States how far away they are from the closest lying subject.
        If lying, states how far away they are from the closest ghost


        Chef:
        States a character is telling the truth. Will always select lying subjects
        if lying, or honest subjects if telling the truth


        ALL GHOSTS: Disguises
        as a random subject and gives false information


        Wraith: A random
        subject lies'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 2252707102340332701, guid: 07a58fb99198d8f429d06902a541622e, type: 3}
      propertyPath: dialoguept2
      value: 
